<node id="Article 78">
  <data key="d0">Article 78</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 78 outlines confidentiality obligations.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 78 outlines the confidentiality requirements for information obtained by notified bodies.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 78 outlines confidentiality obligations for information and documentation obtained pursuant to the Regulation.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 78 specifies the confidentiality obligations for the information and data obtained during the application of the Regulation.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 78 outlines the confidentiality obligations for the application of the Regulation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-49852a3ba29135f33f5a66d5530afe75&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d94f80b79b953201dabec0b31eb7d1f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1f37fb5090b015fdcce5136a4e131a7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b09e19ff232fc74f764b77ba6bcc3f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85e5d3aebe76250dd5161e123f94c06c</data>
