<node id="Article 79">
  <data key="d0">Article 79</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 79 defines the conditions under which a high-risk AI system is non-compliant.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 79 refers to a procedure under the regulation.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 79 outlines the procedure at the national level for dealing with AI systems presenting a risk.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 79 describes procedures for dealing with non-compliant AI systems.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 79 is a clause within a Regulation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-49852a3ba29135f33f5a66d5530afe75&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6a6be1a6e159da5602b5c2c89e742e39&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b09e19ff232fc74f764b77ba6bcc3f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38169246e9fa46f9e17ff295ac3346d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c5974c0c87096acad0b2aac605ef8802</data>
