  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 8 is part of the Regulation and deals with specific requirements and obligations.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 8 is part of Directive 2014/90/EU.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-afaeda77e104462626d5a0e5a16d6f4e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-06bc0ddf887512f18d0e6f10df7767fa</data>
