<node id="Directive 2014/90/EU">
  <data key="d0">Directive 2014/90/EU</data>
  <data key="d1">regulation</data>
  <data key="d2">Directive 2014/90/EU is a legal act of the European Union.&lt;SEP&gt;Directive 2014/90/EU is a European directive related to Artificial Intelligence systems.&lt;SEP&gt;Directive 2014/90/EU of the European Parliament and of the Council is a European Union directive on marine equipment.&lt;SEP&gt;Directive 2014/90/EU is an EU directive on marine equipment.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-afaeda77e104462626d5a0e5a16d6f4e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20e3935f89fd12712570b2f2200d0cbd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-846d247ae92c7dbe167abacc02bc54d4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4b23dceb665491f7cc28993744bf6190</data>
