<node id="Annex III">
  <data key="d0">Annex III</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Annex III is a section of a document that lists specific categories of high-risk AI systems, which are subject to conformity assessment procedures. This annex is part of a regulatory framework designed to ensure the safety and reliability of these systems. It contains detailed criteria and requirements for the classification of AI systems, including those prohibited practices that require evaluation and reporting on the need for amendments. Annex III provides supplementary information on the specific use cases and testing requirements for high-risk AI systems, ensuring they meet stringent standards before being deployed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9bbabb917a8fd4d1cab0f28da3292879&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-afaeda77e104462626d5a0e5a16d6f4e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d317a57f8826116be7899af7bef32dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d9ca73b5aa4562e502c8b54d80b9091a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bde5afcadc1bd6c8b37d30bd93e7d045&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b09e19ff232fc74f764b77ba6bcc3f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38169246e9fa46f9e17ff295ac3346d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3e2911d860a9f8426e67a536486d6752&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d5febc258257152890296838762d806&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-89493349bc2eb2b0fa14e08d5114b0a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9aeb5afbd1a4b894acf12c446410f902&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79168f0d206aaba1ef1cc580415c53cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85e5d3aebe76250dd5161e123f94c06c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1594971bc99373dadcdc53ec98848241</data>
