<node id="Annex I">
  <data key="d0">Annex I</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Annex I contains the list of Union Harmonisation Legislation that governs the market and services of AI systems.&lt;SEP&gt;Annex I is a document part of the regulatory framework listing Union harmonisation legislation.&lt;SEP&gt;Annex I provides details about harmonisation legislation.&lt;SEP&gt;Annex I includes the list of Union harmonisation legislation based on the New Legislative Framework.&lt;SEP&gt;Annex I is part of Directive (EU) 2020/1828.</data>
