<node id="Article 53">
  <data key="d0">Article 53</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 53 outlines the obligations for providers of general-purpose AI models.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 53 outlines the obligations and responsibilities of providers in terms of technical documentation and compliance.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 53 provides specific obligations that the codes of practice need to cover.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 53 is part of Regulation (EU) 2024/1689.</data>
