<node id="Notified Body">
  <data key="d0">Notified Body</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Notified Body is an organization officially recognized by Member States to conduct conformity assessments, particularly for high-risk AI systems. These bodies are responsible for ensuring compliance with relevant standards and requirements and issuing certificates to verify the conformity of AI systems. They play a crucial role in evaluating and examining technical documentation of AI systems, and their responsibilities are often indicated in promotional materials for these systems. Notified Bodies operate on behalf of the market surveillance authority and are authorized to carry out conformity assessments on behalf of Member States. Their activities include verifying the compliance of AI systems with applicable regulations and assessing their conformance to ensure safety and reliability.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1653367cdfb434518d14a6c8c5b52df8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2cddb0815e714f4234b0eb77a0886db3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd5db792306630e07b4579263bafe09f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8731e04e59e27f8bf0dad80e14b80dfa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2bf04dc1138e594ddbe71572222dd4f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4bd0831e0cdcbfe10ebd94d84d35ece&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79168f0d206aaba1ef1cc580415c53cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2af337ff23074191f5e5e0bdd26073d1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85e5d3aebe76250dd5161e123f94c06c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3235bf9304fec9e624bfd76288a19b57</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828343</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
