<node id="Annex III - Biometric verification">
  <data key="d0">Annex III - Biometric verification</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Biometric verification is a specific type of biometric system, which is intended for confirming a person's identity, and is not covered under high-risk AI systems according to Annex III.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-846d247ae92c7dbe167abacc02bc54d4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828343</data>
