<node id="AI Office">
  <data key="d0">AI Office</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">AI Office is the Commission's function responsible for implementing and monitoring AI systems. It plays a crucial role in developing and recommending voluntary model terms for contracts between providers of high-risk AI systems and third parties. Furthermore, the AI Office is tasked with creating templates to facilitate compliance with fundamental rights impact assessments. It is also involved in issuing technical documentation and templates for model training and usage. Additionally, AI Office oversees compliance of AI systems, has powers similar to market surveillance authorities, and can request the Commission to update guidelines. 

The AI Office is an entity established by the Commission to support the AI regulatory framework, providing secretariat for the Board, convening meetings, and preparing the agenda. It also provides coordination support for joint investigations and oversees the implementation of tasks, receiving and acting on alerts concerning AI models. The AI Office is responsible for promoting and regulating AI technologies, receiving and processing information and documentation from providers of AI models, and ensuring compliance with the Regulation. 

Furthermore, AI Office encourages, facilitates, and ensures the creation and monitoring of codes of practice, as well as providing support and guidance for AI regulatory sandboxes. It is also tasked with the development of methodologies for evaluating risk levels of AI systems, which are to be included in Annex III. The AI Office assists the Scientific Panel for tasks related to the Union safeguard procedure and other activities.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7ab695e67854c29668d30835afc8fa56&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d317a57f8826116be7899af7bef32dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d9ca73b5aa4562e502c8b54d80b9091a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91245f3945c3d7cc7ebcd77b066b7ef9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6a6be1a6e159da5602b5c2c89e742e39&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64f96fb4c623fd44d4b9931460dfb273&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d94f80b79b953201dabec0b31eb7d1f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1f37fb5090b015fdcce5136a4e131a7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95f4bd1a2188c8af0ad581dae55c8d76&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-414727d1a6d237ecc9306035920d4685&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ba7997e7cc9a9c81f53126131569e4a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-51ee6686c61ba5ea54245e3aa87b1783&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b46993509f7f45efc7114ce53d7712a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-351f07fc1cfb91436e9dffcf5c8e88df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-06bc0ddf887512f18d0e6f10df7767fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f39b62663d19c447e94b4bea8e9c4db&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83ff9251c686ac1ddd5ef4f93316b9a8</data>
