<node id="Border Control Management">
  <data key="d0">Border Control Management</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Border Control Management involves the regulation and enforcement of border crossing rules and regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Border Control Management is the process of regulating and controlling the entry and exit of persons to and from a country.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-33b3b690e83a48d4f90c85be3eebb646&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-89493349bc2eb2b0fa14e08d5114b0a5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828346</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="High-Risk AI System">
  <data key="d0">High-Risk AI System</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">High-Risk AI System is a sophisticated artificial intelligence system that poses significant safety or privacy risks. It is subject to strict documentation, monitoring, and regulatory requirements. These systems are considered to have a high potential impact and require special assessments and controls. High-Risk AI Systems may include AI systems listed in Annex III and those that could have significant legal effects or impact health, safety, or fundamental rights. They must meet specific requirements and comply with certain obligations, necessitating special monitoring and compliance checks to ensure safety and compliance with regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-64f96fb4c623fd44d4b9931460dfb273&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1f37fb5090b015fdcce5136a4e131a7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38169246e9fa46f9e17ff295ac3346d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd5db792306630e07b4579263bafe09f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-51ee6686c61ba5ea54245e3aa87b1783&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ef9991e58e018e79ec133e41dd155972&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4bd0831e0cdcbfe10ebd94d84d35ece&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9aeb5afbd1a4b894acf12c446410f902&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2af337ff23074191f5e5e0bdd26073d1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-afaeda77e104462626d5a0e5a16d6f4e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828346</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
