  <data key="d2">Delegated Acts are acts adopted by the Commission to amend the conditions in the regulation.&lt;SEP&gt;Delegated acts are official documents that amend the list of high-risk AI systems.&lt;SEP&gt;Delegated acts are specific acts that are delegated to certain bodies for implementation.</data>
