<node id="CE Marking">
  <data key="d0">CE Marking</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">CE Marking is a marking affixed to digital high-risk AI systems, accessible via an interface or an easily accessible machine-readable code.&lt;SEP&gt;CE Marking is a marking required for products sold within the European Economic Area to denote they comply with EU directives.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c5974c0c87096acad0b2aac605ef8802&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3235bf9304fec9e624bfd76288a19b57</data>
