<node id="EU Database">
  <data key="d0">EU Database</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The EU Database is a system where providers and deployers register high-risk AI systems and their usage.&lt;SEP&gt;The EU Database is a secure non-public section of the European Union for storing information about AI systems.&lt;SEP&gt;EU Database is an official database for the registration of products.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c5974c0c87096acad0b2aac605ef8802&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-89493349bc2eb2b0fa14e08d5114b0a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3235bf9304fec9e624bfd76288a19b57</data>
