  <data key="d0">Official Journal of the European Union</data>
  <data key="d1">reference</data>
  <data key="d2">Official Journal of the European Union is the official document where references to relevant harmonised standards and related criteria are published.&lt;SEP&gt;The Official Journal of the European Union is the official gazette of the European Union where conformity assessments are published.&lt;SEP&gt;Official Journal of the European Union is a publication that lists harmonised standards.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bd5db792306630e07b4579263bafe09f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-612e9d6ebed2e9c1601b0ed553a37ca2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79168f0d206aaba1ef1cc580415c53cf</data>
