  <data key="d1">legal_reference</data>
  <data key="d2">Recommendation 2003/361/EC is a European Union legal document guiding the size and structure of enterprises.&lt;SEP&gt;Recommendation 2003/361/EC is a document that defines the criteria for microenterprises.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bd5db792306630e07b4579263bafe09f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-351f07fc1cfb91436e9dffcf5c8e88df</data>
