<node id="Chapter III, Section 2">
  <data key="d0">Chapter III, Section 2</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Chapter III, Section 2 contains specific requirements for AI systems.&lt;SEP&gt;Chapter III, Section 2 outlines the requirements for the validation and testing procedures of AI systems.&lt;SEP&gt;Chapter III, Section 2 refers to the specific section in the relevant regulation or directive detailing requirements for the AI system.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-612e9d6ebed2e9c1601b0ed553a37ca2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4bd0831e0cdcbfe10ebd94d84d35ece&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4b23dceb665491f7cc28993744bf6190</data>
