  <data key="d2">The advisory forum is consulted by the Commission when drafting common specifications.&lt;SEP&gt;Advisory Forum is a group established to provide technical expertise and advice to the Board and Commission under Regulation (EU) 2019/1020.&lt;SEP&gt;The Advisory Forum is an entity that sets rules of procedure, elects co-chairs, and holds meetings. It also prepares reports and may invite stakeholders.</data>
