<node id="article 14">
  <data key="d0">article 14</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 14 is part of a set of guidelines for high-risk AI systems, focusing on human oversight, including design and measures for preventing or minimizing risks.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-83433e14f479755aaaf16c96e5408e58</data>
