  <data key="d5">1779828350</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="肠胃不适">
  <data key="d0">肠胃不适</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Gastrointestinal discomfort may be related to side effects or issues with technology or data processes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4b23dceb665491f7cc28993744bf6190</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828350</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="risk">
  <data key="d0">risk</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Risk is the combination of the probability of harm and the severity of that harm.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5303a356a94e477f040c55c8fb0446c1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828350</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="provider">
  <data key="d0">provider</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">A provider is a natural or legal person, public authority, agency, or other body that develops an AI system or a general-purpose AI model and places it on the market or puts it into service.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5303a356a94e477f040c55c8fb0446c1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828350</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="deployer">
  <data key="d0">deployer</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">A deployer is a natural or legal person, public authority, agency, or other body using an AI system under its authority, except where the AI system is used in the course of a personal non-professional activity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5303a356a94e477f040c55c8fb0446c1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828350</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="authorised representative">
  <data key="d0">authorised representative</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">An authorised representative is a natural or legal person located or established in the Union who has received and accepted a written mandate from a provider of an AI system or a general-purpose AI model.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5303a356a94e477f040c55c8fb0446c1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828350</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="importer">
  <data key="d0">importer</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">An importer is a natural or legal person located or established in the Union that places on the market an AI system bearing the name or trademark of an entity from a third country.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5303a356a94e477f040c55c8fb0446c1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828350</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="distributor">
  <data key="d0">distributor</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">A distributor is a natural or legal person in the supply chain, other than the provider or the importer, that makes an AI system available on the Union market.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5303a356a94e477f040c55c8fb0446c1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828350</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="operator">
  <data key="d0">operator</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">An operator is a provider, product manufacturer, deployer, authorised representative, importer, or distributor.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5303a356a94e477f040c55c8fb0446c1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828350</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="placing on the market">
  <data key="d0">placing on the market</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Placing on the market is the first making available of an AI system or a general-purpose AI model on the Union market.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5303a356a94e477f040c55c8fb0446c1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828350</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="making available on the market">
  <data key="d0">making available on the market</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Making available on the market is the supply of an AI system or a general-purpose AI model for distribution or use on the Union market in the course of a commercial activity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5303a356a94e477f040c55c8fb0446c1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828350</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="putting into service">
  <data key="d0">putting into service</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Putting into service is the supply of an AI system for first use directly to a deployer or for own use in the Union for its intended purpose.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5303a356a94e477f040c55c8fb0446c1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828350</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="intended purpose">
  <data key="d0">intended purpose</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Intended purpose refers to the use for which an AI system is intended by the provider, including the specific context and conditions of use.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5303a356a94e477f040c55c8fb0446c1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828350</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="reasonably foreseeable misuse">
  <data key="d0">reasonably foreseeable misuse</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Reasonably foreseeable misuse occurs when an AI system is used in a way not in accordance with its intended purpose, due to human behavior or interaction with other systems.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5303a356a94e477f040c55c8fb0446c1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828350</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="safety component">
  <data key="d0">safety component</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">A safety component is a part of an AI system or product that performs a safety function and whose failure endangers health and safety.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5303a356a94e477f040c55c8fb0446c1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828350</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="instructions for use">
  <data key="d0">instructions for use</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Instructions for use are provided by the provider to inform the deployer about the intended purpose and proper use of an AI system.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5303a356a94e477f040c55c8fb0446c1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828350</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="recall of an AI system">
  <data key="d0">recall of an AI system</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Recall of an AI system is a measure to return the AI system to the provider or disable its use.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5303a356a94e477f040c55c8fb0446c1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779828350</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
