<edge source="Article 51(1), point (a)" target="Commission">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Commission uses the criteria in Article 51(1), point (a) to designate general-purpose AI models with systemic risk.&lt;SEP&gt;The Commission shall take into account the criteria set out in Article 51(1), point (a).</data>
