  <data key="d8">The AI Office works closely with the Commission to promote and regulate AI technologies.&lt;SEP&gt;The Commission develops Union expertise and capabilities in AI through the AI Office.&lt;SEP&gt;The Commission is requested to update guidelines in response to requests from the AI Office.&lt;SEP&gt;The AI Office develops methodologies for evaluating risk levels guided by the Commission.</data>
  <data key="d9">expertise development,guidance,methodology development,promotion,regulation,support,updates</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-4d317a57f8826116be7899af7bef32dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d9ca73b5aa4562e502c8b54d80b9091a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-351f07fc1cfb91436e9dffcf5c8e88df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-06bc0ddf887512f18d0e6f10df7767fa</data>
