<edge source="Commission" target="AI Regulatory Sandbox">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Commission shall take the annual reports into account when exercising its tasks under the AI regulatory sandbox framework.&lt;SEP&gt;The Commission is responsible for developing and overseeing AI regulatory sandboxes.</data>
