  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Commission can enter into consultations with the relevant Member State where objections are raised against an authorization issued by a different Member State.&lt;SEP&gt;Market Surveillance Authorities inform the Commission about evaluation results and actions taken.</data>
