<edge source="Provider" target="High-Risk AI System">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The initial provider must provide necessary information and technical access to new providers when the AI system is no longer considered a provider's responsibility.&lt;SEP&gt;Providers must ensure High-Risk AI Systems comply with regulations and take corrective actions.&lt;SEP&gt;The Provider develops and ensures compliance of the high-risk AI system.</data>
