<edge source="Provider" target="Union Technical Documentation Assessment Certificate">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Union Technical Documentation Assessment Certificate certifies that the Provider's AI System is in conformity with the relevant requirements.&lt;SEP&gt;The Provider submits necessary information to obtain a Union Technical Documentation Assessment Certificate.</data>
  <data key="d9">certification,registration</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-f4bd0831e0cdcbfe10ebd94d84d35ece</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1779828358</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Provider" target="Notified Body">
  <data key="d7">6.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The notified body is responsible for the conformity assessment procedures and the affixing of the identification number for CE marking.&lt;SEP&gt;The Notified Body assesses the Provider's AI system and issues a Union Technical Documentation Assessment Certificate.&lt;SEP&gt;The Notified Body examines the technical documentation and conducts tests on the AI System provided by the Provider.&lt;SEP&gt;The Notified Body assesses changes to the AI System and decides if a new conformity assessment is required.&lt;SEP&gt;The Provider informs the Notified Body about any changes to the AI System that may affect its compliance.&lt;SEP&gt;Providers must submit to the Notified Body for certification and compliance verification.</data>
  <data key="d9">CE marking,assessment,certification,change assessment,compliance,conformity assessment,oversight</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-f4bd0831e0cdcbfe10ebd94d84d35ece&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2af337ff23074191f5e5e0bdd26073d1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3235bf9304fec9e624bfd76288a19b57</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1779828359</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
