<edge source="Notified Body" target="Conformity Assessment Body">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Conformity Assessment Bodies may perform activities only when the Commission and Member States do not raise objections.&lt;SEP&gt;Notified Bodies are recognized to conduct conformity assessments for high-risk AI systems.</data>
  <data key="d9">authorization,objection,recognition,relationship</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-2cddb0815e714f4234b0eb77a0886db3</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1779828355</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Notified Body" target="Notifying Authority">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Notified Bodies must ensure independence from high-risk AI system providers and document their independence.&lt;SEP&gt;Notified Bodies shall report to the Notifying Authorities on their activities and any changes, and Notifying Authorities shall investigate and take action if necessary.&lt;SEP&gt;Notifying Authorities shall monitor and ensure the continued compliance of notified bodies and take action if necessary.</data>
  <data key="d9">compliance,documentation,independence,monitoring,reporting</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-2cddb0815e714f4234b0eb77a0886db3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd5db792306630e07b4579263bafe09f</data>
