<edge source="Notified Body" target="High-Risk AI System">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Notified Bodies are responsible for verifying the conformity of high-risk AI systems according to specific procedures.&lt;SEP&gt;The Notified Body assesses the high-risk AI system to ensure it meets the required standards.</data>
  <data key="d9">assess,certification,compliance,verification</data>
